Name: Void Breach
About the game: Explore a world beyond the cosmic horizon. Travel through the forest of eternal night, to haunted mansions and deserted castles, from mountain peaks to the bottom of the sea. Search for your daughter before she is forever lost in the void. Follow the clues and bring her back to earth. To safety. Go quickly! Already the enigmatic entity that shadows the world threatens to claims her. Extra content! The soundtrack comes bundled with the game. Features: A mysterious world on the edge of space. A killer soundtrack. Whimsical characters from the farthest reaches of the void. Puzzles! (They make sense.) Low res, colorful pixel art filled with character. A story of mystery and exploration, and regret. Character portraits!
